cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.SD, cs.HC 

Reasoning: 
- cs.CL (Computation and Language) is the most likely category as the paper is about training a personalized dialogue system using transfer learning and reinforcement learning. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is also likely as the paper proposes a novel approach to transfer knowledge between different users while keeping personal preferences intact. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is relevant as the paper uses deep learning models and reinforcement learning to train the personalized decoder. 
- cs.SD (Software Engineering) is less likely but still possible as the paper discusses the implementation and evaluation of the proposed personalized decoder model. 
- cs.HC (Human-Computer Interaction) is also less likely but relevant as the paper aims to improve the user experience of task-oriented dialogue systems by personalizing the responses.
